data.description: Escape to your tranquil retreat in Nashville! A charming home with several nostalgic features.  This home offers a serene sanctuary from the city's bustle while remaining conveniently close to the vibrant pulse! Three bedrooms with a den that features a built-in desk and bookshelves and served as a large primary suite for the previous owner.  The walkout basement provides another bonus room off a huge utility room and comes with all appliances/washer/dryer.   New HVAC in 2020! Newer fridge, gas hot water heater, completely updated plumbing, three-car carport, basketball court, fully-fenced lot, ranch-style living, easy to open or make your own changes! Pre-inspected and ready to move in!
